# zappy

A entire world represented by a server and graphics and its inhabitants by a script.

## Installation && Tools

Just need to run 'make' on linux system.</br>

## Usage

./zappy_server [-p port][-x world_x] [-y wolrd_y][-c max_client] [-t speed]-n team_name_1 team_name_2 ...
./zappy_ai [-n team-name] [-p port] [-h machine-name] or ./launch_ai.sh [NB_IA]

